# Ignore everything by default — only allow what the Docker build actually
# needs (see Dockerfile's COPY lines). Simpler than maintaining a deny-list,
# and doesn't silently rot when files move (scripts/*.sh here used to
# reference paths that no longer exist after scripts/builds/ was split out).
*

!scripts/
!scripts/builds/
!scripts/builds/**
!claude-defaults/
!claude-defaults/**
